title: Newton leads late Carolina rally for 27-23 win over Seattle
text:
> North Carolina Newton leads late Carolina rally for 27-23 win over Seattle Seattle Seahawks' Cliff Avril (56) celebrates after a play as Carolina Panthers' Jonathan Stewart (28) gets up from the turf in the second half of an NFL football game, Sunday, Oct. 18, 2015, in Seattle. (AP Photo/Elaine Thompson)
